🎥 Tubed.pro - YouTube Summary Tool
Enhance the YouTube viewing experience by providing concise summaries of video content. Key features and benefits include:

⏱️ Time-Saving: Quickly grasp the main points of YouTube videos without watching them in full.
📈 Efficiency: Ideal for researchers, students, and professionals who need to process large amounts of video information.
🔍 Content Overview: Get a snapshot of video content to determine relevance before committing to watch.
📖 Accessibility: Makes video content more accessible by providing text-based summaries.
💬 Get full transcript of a video
🔥 Roast any video (funny feature made for lols)

🚀 Tubed.pro aims to revolutionize how users interact with YouTube content, making information consumption more efficient and tailored to individual needs.
